IMPORTANT — read alongside the warranty disclaimer above.

This project concerns suicide and psychological crisis. It is released into the
public domain so it can help as widely as possible. It is NOT a clinical tool, a
medical device, a diagnosis, or a guarantee of safety. Nothing here makes an AI
safe by itself. Anyone deploying it in a real product must pair it with people
who have genuine crisis and clinical expertise, and with current, locale-correct
crisis resources. Shipping it as a "safety net" it cannot be is itself a harm.
See README.md, "Honesty — read this before you trust any of it."

